      "course": "CSC510",
      "source_file": "week3_rectree-510.pdf",
      "chunk_index": 5,
      "chunk_in_page": 0,
      "page": 6,
      "slide": null,
      "text": "Recursion Substitution is kind of hard to understand… T(n) = 2T(n/2) + cn = 2(2T(n/4)+cn/2) + cn = 2(2(2T(n/8)+cn/4)+cn/2) + cn … = … T(1) ..."
